{"tid":1358403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(  推畀港鐵同乗客知 ) 點解要癱瘓地鐵","createTime":"2019-07-24T02:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T03:43:31.000Z","uid":265766,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3f9eb627852869af19bc2550879bbf1902b8f0df","tid":1358403,"uid":265766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:19:22.000Z","msg":"港鐵就元朗站恐怖襲擊只強烈譴責暴力事件， 但對於警方的處理態度隻字不提 。<br />\n警察是有鐵路應變部隊, 受到通報後，隊伍亦承諾9分鐘內趕到現場。處理影響鐵路系統的恐怖襲擊及其他重大事故. <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">昨日元朗港鐵恐襲, 絕對有機會在其他港九線發生!</span></span></strong><br />\n港鐵必須就事件強烈要求警方回應及堅守鐵路應變部隊的承諾.  否則乘客會因自身安全而對港鐵失信心<br />\n<br />\n為著日後公眾安全, 今早要癱瘓地鐵, 請大家體諒<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mtrhk/posts/10162408341270151\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmtrhk%2Fposts%2F10162408341270151&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1YeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=e3820dbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mtrhk/posts/10162408341270151</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Akm1He.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Akm1He.png&h=3ed3ef63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1126/chi/7476.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F1126%2Fchi%2F7476.html&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1YeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=39a3507a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1126/chi/7476.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OEEV5ZZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOEEV5ZZ.png&h=0a276764&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75f6436cce5648a3131215d9fbbd15b3b59a7dad","tid":1358403,"uid":165246,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:20:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"7b0853c650af9156fcba77f260eb2c6f302cc910","tid":1358403,"uid":265766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:23:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fa02b9e10ae7a1bc45401dd3931f5b5f405078b1","tid":1358403,"uid":265766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:36:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1962562fda77ac7279ef5ffcc5d67c35f350b2e6","tid":1358403,"uid":122676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:38:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"792193d3ef4fbb3e92c3667de81a336e8371f7a8","tid":1358403,"uid":265766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:42:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"05188519fd54deb6e8184baac2aee8dd5350c323","tid":1358403,"uid":265766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:56:24.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"bc169a41d69793ffe657747b1a5dc1115d52c067","tid":1358403,"uid":276215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4dff8faf6063bb6a54fb1f550842a34d124675","tid":1358403,"uid":276215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.